for code in tqdm(stock_list['종목코드'].values[:3]):
    data = fdr.DataReader(code, start = start_date, end = end_date)[['Close']].reset_index()
    data = pd.merge(Business_days, data, how = 'outer')
    data['weekday'] = data.Date.apply(lambda x : x.weekday())
    data['weeknum'] = data.Date.apply(lambda x : x.strftime('%V'))
    data.Close = data.Close.ffill()
    
    data['Date'] = data['Date'].astype('str')
    data = pd.merge(data, df, on='Date')
    
    stock_name = stock_list.loc[stock_list['종목코드'] == code, '종목명'].values
    plt.figure(figsize=(12,10))
    plt.xticks(fontsize=15)
    plt.yticks(fontsize=15)
    plt.title(f'{stock_name[0]}', fontdict={'fontsize':20})
    sns.heatmap(data.corr(), cmap='Blues', annot=True, fmt='.2f', cbar=False, annot_kws={"size": 20})

for code in tqdm(stock_list['종목코드'].values):
    data = fdr.DataReader(code, start=start_date, end=end_date)[['Close']].reset_index()
    data = pd.merge(Business_days, data, how = 'outer')
    data.Close = data.Close.interpolate()
    if stock_list.loc[stock_list['종목코드']==code, '상장시장'].values == 'KOSPI':
        stock_sum['KOSPI_sum'] += data['Close']
    else:
        stock_sum['KOSDAQ_sum'] += data['Close']
